#                                                                                                                                                                                                       

[media]

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

[media]

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

[media]

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

[media]

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!

[media]

**Christmas Update**
- New Xmas Battlepass
- Christmas Ornament Hunt
- New Rudolf Bundle
- Christmas Themed Levels

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/499303746_2181339939044468_540727540857874572_n.mp4?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=qur_l8g__3IQ7kNvwHJbiww&_nc_oc=Admc0IUXNW_eSA9K_g6qsaY1Xpp5TnXehUFJ7Pg6xVdN1a2NLXONCAGUJqz2cbfKG1g&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=e2Se9sJugmwFKvmTso7ggA&oh=00_AfpzTt_PVpE1Kb6USnVpJBZ51FZoRJshuIzV9m26WZqbfg&oe=697F8B64)

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/491830888_1234204841304584_7133986973260987280_n.mp4?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=8LXC_3x9OIYQ7kNvwG1wHU_&_nc_oc=AdkxfVC6GMastgHUc2zQoCMQ2Mv1AsachiAcrLsOSF19HdGb1oLrpGeG65ByNIZEu0I&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=e2Se9sJugmwFKvmTso7ggA&oh=00_AfoJA5mkgUHW96kVMdxEdIsu0s7gTCPBwXTNenVzr2vP_w&oe=697F91BC)

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/491821117_1430846481437060_8099142216261706884_n.mp4?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=VDXJe08HlacQ7kNvwGaVTZ4&_nc_oc=Adkqo7FckTRqVntdV2SyG8K0x5UvkQg0uc49gPLVf7ynbSGKz5CDGsX-o9S3vTSagjA&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=e2Se9sJugmwFKvmTso7ggA&oh=00_AfqOR6Ac_bxMiJ-6tnleyzS0wIlKIXZpCsOUNCE6aukggA&oe=697F808C)

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!

![{"height":1440,"type":"image","width":2560}](https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/499292426_757548860702625_520424425045914625_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vvkHq94_yugQ7kNvwEGOdrY&_nc_oc=AdnNoSeHFuB9ENCEyiXrM6rMfYc2g3x1VMZy8dupcbF760k53capmUY1pKFZpjDqUpg&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AfqUueSiaqW7LeUmdV2LmtI49StxsSPgKfq-0D8t6-dSsQ&oe=697F7DF2)
